explore

public void explore()
Creates and executes new sequences in a loop, using the sequences in s. New sequences are themselves added to s. Stops when timer says it's testtime to stop.

subsumed_sequences

public Set<Sequence> subsumed_sequences()
Returns the set of sequences that are used as inputs in other sequences (and can thus be thought of as subsumed by another sequence). This should only be called for subclasses that support this.
